name: ELEFANCLUB 01
description:
A weekly original illustration for collectors of Les Elefants Terribles. 

"Splashlesinger big party, 
lifting the skin of the water.
Oscar breakfast with Brandy Rollergraham, 
she’s in love with a dead guy.
Venice swimpainting in 47, 
let’s toot it up, do the crybaby.
One word… just one word.
Plastics."

Rotring pen and markers on paper

Follow @elefants_tez on twitter
